                        <interp inst="t18391125-name-295" type="given" value="ROBERT DANIEL"></interp>ROBERT DANIEL NICHOLLS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a furniture-broker, and live in Brook<lb></lb>hill, Clerkenwell. The prisoner was my errand-boy between two and three months—I allowed him to receive money on my account—he ought to account to me as soon as he received it—he did not account to me on the 26th of October for 25<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—his mother called on me four or five hours after he received it, and said he had lost part of the money.</p>
